
## pi-manager (Swarm manager + observability)
- Grafana
- Prometheus
- Blackbox exporter (HTTP/ICMP/DNS probes)
- Speedtest exporter (bandwidth snapshot)
- Pi-hole (DNS redundancy)
- Portainer
- node-exporter

## pi-worker-1 (DNS + encoding)
- Pi-hole (primary DNS)
- Media encoding worker
- node-exporter

## pi-worker-2 (media)
- Plex
- Transmission
- node-exporter
- External USB storage

## pi-worker-3 (database)
- PostgreSQL
- Postgres exporter
- node-exporter

## ops-runner (automation)
- Agent Host (internal API)
- Local LLMs: **Mistral + Llama**
- Agent Runner (scheduled briefs + webhook receiver)
